at the counterterm is definitely local. In this sense,\nstring theories can be consistently defined in generalized supergravity\nbackgrounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 17:19:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-30"}
