ble of entities. The ability of\nestablish trust through permissioned blockchains enables to move the control\nfrom the datacenters to the edge, truly realizing the promises of edge-centric\ncomputing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Apr 2019 07:59:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
